text: 00:01 Learning generative AI without machine learning or deep learning 01:19 Learning the basics before jumping into generative AI is important. 02:33 Python is a prerequisite for directly using generative AI APIs. 03:41 It's good to learn machine learning basics before diving into generative AI. 04:47 Deep learning basics are crucial for interviews 05:54 Basic knowledge of statistics and machine learning concepts is essential for working on LLM projects. 07:07 Learning generative AI alone may not be sufficient for interviews. 08:19 Basics in machine learning and deep learning are essential before diving into generative AI.
